modShortDescription: Tired of seeing only Lumberjack Zombies in the snow biome? Then this mod is for you. This 7 Days to Die mod adds normal zombie spawns to the snow biome.
modDescription:
Tired of seeing only Lumberjack Zombies in the snow biome? Then this mod is for you. This 7 Days to Die mod adds normal [zombie](https://7daystodiemods.com/zombie-mods/) spawns to the snow biome.

[Download](https://yehonal.github.io/DownGit/#/home?url=https://github.com/TSBX-7D/Modlets/tree/master/TSBX_snowZombieVariety)

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/8169-tsbx-collection/).

**Credits:** [TSBX](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/tsbx/)
